WEBVTT

00:08.050 --> 00:09.670
Previously on Cloak and Dagger...

00:09.690 --> 00:10.766
We're just taking back what's ours.

00:10.790 --> 00:12.056
- Tyrone?
- Duane?

00:12.080 --> 00:13.760
- Look at you!
- So you own this place?

00:13.800 --> 00:15.499
What if you could get
Connors on something else?

00:15.500 --> 00:16.500
Like dealing drugs?

00:16.510 --> 00:18.139
He cleared the field for

00:18.140 --> 00:19.979
a mystery dealer to play monopoly.

00:19.980 --> 00:21.900
I don't work for you. We're partners.

00:21.960 --> 00:23.576
Partner is not the word
you're looking for!

00:23.600 --> 00:25.320
Not after the night you shot my boy.

00:25.400 --> 00:26.650
ROXXON is placing the blame

00:26.670 --> 00:28.900
of the oil rig explosion on Nathan.

00:28.940 --> 00:31.060
I've been looking at
my dad's old papers.

00:31.100 --> 00:32.439
Trying to connect the dots.

00:32.500 --> 00:33.780
My name is Mina Hess,

00:33.810 --> 00:35.979
and I'm working with ROXXON Gulf

00:35.980 --> 00:37.080
to save the world.

00:42.300 --> 00:43.700
So, we're doing a reading?

00:46.200 --> 00:48.460
How go things with that boy of yours?

00:48.540 --> 00:50.940
- He's not mine.
- He's yours enough.

00:51.700 --> 00:53.220
Is this your way of having "the talk?"

00:53.280 --> 00:54.940
Cause you're kinda predicting the past.

00:58.800 --> 01:00.140
This reading ain't for you.

01:00.840 --> 01:02.510
It's for this city of ours.

01:02.540 --> 01:04.019
So, what's wrong with the city?

01:05.580 --> 01:07.680
Shit goes down from time to time.

01:10.720 --> 01:12.520
And why do you need me?

01:12.550 --> 01:14.520
I ain't smellin' sex on you,

01:14.980 --> 01:16.780
but a connection to a power.

01:17.180 --> 01:18.720
The power I felt in that boy.

01:18.760 --> 01:20.560
What does Tyrone have
to do with anything?

01:20.590 --> 01:22.040
I don't know yet.

01:22.120 --> 01:23.980
That's what the reading is for.

01:24.340 --> 01:26.720
First, we look at the past.

01:28.340 --> 01:29.820
Then, the present.

01:30.800 --> 01:33.440
And if the Loa are with us today,

01:33.620 --> 01:35.570
we'll see...

01:36.820 --> 01:37.920
the future.

